te=1973-06-10 | accessdate=2021-04-03 |quote= }}</ref>，同年在電影《[[亡命浪子|亡命浪子]]》中首次飾演女主角，与電影紅星[[鄧光榮|鄧光榮]]演對手戲<ref>{{cite news | title=潘冰嫦不肯接吻 鄧光榮點到為止 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2F3zFhASdgu4WuI%2FZK9MGsT&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=2&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=4 | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1973-07-23 | accessdate=2021-04-03 |quote= }}</ref>。至1977年，潘冰嫦約滿離開麗的電視，又提前與[[無綫電視|無綫電視]]解約<ref>{{cite news | title=潘冰嫦台演紫娟 提前與無綫解約 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgIn67zeQZtWv&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=7&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=9 | publisher=香港工商日報