1981年，潘冰嫦約滿離開邵氏，之後輾轉於香港和[[台灣|台灣]]之間，繼續發展演藝事業。同期為香港《華僑日報》以及加拿大《[[大漢公報|大漢公報]]》撰寫專欄<ref>{{cite news | title=專欄 - 好聲好氣 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%A5%8A%E6%8C%AF%E8%80%80&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%A5%8A%E6%8C%AF%E8%80%80%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%A5%8A%E6%8C%AF%E8%80%80%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%A5%8A%E6%8C%AF%E8%80%80%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%A5%8A%E6%8C%AF%E8%80%80%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%A5%8A%E6%8C%AF%E8%80%80%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%A5%8A%E6%8C%AF%E8%80%80%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BakvA8rFW5EvaKmHNt3qgg&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=12&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=14  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1987-04-08 | accessdate=2021-04-03 |quote= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=專欄 - 芳草冰心 | url=http://chinesetimes.lib.sfu.ca/ctimes-252589/page-12 | page= | publisher=大漢公報 | date=1991-12-10 | accessdate=2021-04-03 |quote= }}</ref>。也在[[香港商業電台|香港商業電台]]主持《東南西北》<ref>{{cite news | title=商業一台新年聯歡 潘冰嫦不敢拍戲 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FYxWHIw1Z7kaG2GqtwR3Wh&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=209&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=16 | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1987-01-04 | accessdate=2021-04-04 |quote= }}</ref>。1980年代後期起，潘冰嫦先後在[[亞洲電視|亞洲電視]]和[[無線電視|無線電視]]演出電視劇及主持節目。也曾主持香港電台廣播節目環節《霓嫦物語》{{noteTag|name=安哥同學會}}。1996年得到他人指點，指其名字中的「嫦（娥）」奔月的舉動很孤單，不利當時有男友的她，便建議她改藝名「潘碧常」<ref>{{cite news | title=潘冰嫦 易名潘碧常 | url= | page= | publisher=新明日報 | date=1996-11-09 | accessdate=2021-04-14 |quote= }}</ref>。本來打算息影的她基於[[陳寶華|陳寶華]]看過其《真情》的演出，於是被對方遊說重投亞洲電視，在2001年6月開始成了基本合約演員<ref>{{cite news | title=潘冰嫦 與施明茶敍 | url=http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/apple/20010614/C16-08.html | page= | publisher=香港蘋果日報 | date=2001-06-14 | accessdate=2021-04-14 | quote= | archive-date=2021-04-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414134241/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/apple/20010614/C16-08.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。淡出娛樂圈後，潘冰嫦活躍於參與慈善[[義工|義工]]工作<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hospicecare.cloudhost8.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/SPHC-40-Newsletter.pdf |title=會訊第40期  |date=2007-04 |website= |publisher=善寧會 |access-date=2021-04-03 |quote=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hospicecare.org.hk/uploadedFile/SPHC-56-Newsletter.pdf |title=會訊第50期 |date=2015-08 |website= |publisher=善寧會 |access-date=2021-04-03 |quote= |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925134817/https://www.hospicecare.org.hk/uploadedFile/SPHC-56-Newsletter.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，又會客串演出電視短劇<ref>{{cite web |url=http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzYwNjUzNDA4.html |title=亞視百人-潘冰嫦 |date=2012-03-01 |website= |publisher=亞洲電視 |access-date=2021-04-03 |quote= |archive-date=2019-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205041202/https://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzYwNjUzNDA4.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而她淡出娛樂圈的原因在於約滿電視台之前被圈中人的謠言中傷，以致不獲電視台高層與她續約{{noteTag|name=安哥同學會}}。

==家庭生活==
潘冰嫦於1999年結婚<ref>{{cite news | title=潘冰嫦情人節搞派對 | url=http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/hkdn/20000213/B04006.html | page= | publisher=新報 | date=2000-02-13 | accessdate=2021-04-15 | quote= | archive-date=2021-04-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414135435/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/hkdn/20000213/B04006.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，丈夫為[[東蓮覺苑|東蓮覺苑]]董事兼[[寶覺小學|寶覺小學]]辦學團體校董譚溢鴻<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pokokps.edu.hk/imc/imc.html |title=二零二零至二零二一年度法團校董會 |date= |website= |publisher=寶覺小學 |access-date=2021-04-03 |quote= |archive-date=2012-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121221193052/http://www.pokokps.edu.hk/imc/imc.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=香港傑出女性先鋒──張蓮覺居士 | url=https://www.buddhistdoor.org/tc/mingkok/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%82%91%E5%87%BA%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E5%85%88%E9%8B%92%E5%BC%B5%E8%93%AE%E8%A6%BA%E5%B1%85%E5%A3%AB | page= | publisher=佛門網 | date=2012-04-05 | accessdate=2021-04-03 |quote= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=我校舉行福慧基金會獎學金頒獎典禮 | url=https://www.zqy.com/xiaozhang/article/72/6018 | page= | publisher= | date=2015-06-03 | accessdate=2021-04-03 |quote= }}</ref>。二人婚後育有一子。此外，她與已故歌手[[鄧麗君|鄧麗君]]是好朋友<ref>{{cite news | title=潘冰嫦不賺走埠錢 施思男友暫仍保密 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%BD%98%E5%86%B0%E5%AB%A6%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgJMaw3I1DwHu&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet